"25:67:7" : {s: 25, a: 67, w: 7, r: "قتر", t: "يَقْتُرُوا۟", l: "يَقْتُرُ", lc: 1, tl: "yaqturū", lb: "",e: "and are not stingy", b: "তারা কার্পণ্য করে (নি)", i: "mereka kikir", f: 1, rm: "to be stingy, tight-fisted, niggardly, have scantily, be barely sufficient (sustenance), give bare sustenance. qatarun & qataratun - dust, gloom (of sorrow), darkness, stinginess. qaturun - niggardly. muqtirun - to be in reduced circumstances, straitened."},
